# Belly of the Fishy Beast

- Based on the [Belly of the Fishy Beast](https://dreamingdragonslayer.itch.io/belly-of-the-fishy-beast2) by [Dreaming Dragonslayer](https://dreamingdragonslayer.com).
- Conversion by [Gordon](https://magisterical.itch.io/]

## General Notes
- Put any notes on the conversion here!
- You can list monsters & NPCs separately or by the location they can be found

