## Locations
### Stomach
#### Green Stomach Acid
- d6 STR damage if touched

Chanting Squid Man: stats as Mind Lasher

Leather Bat Wing Creatures: 4HP, 0 ARM, 10 STR, 14 DEX, 12 WIL, bite (d6) 

Fish-Man Guards: 8HP, 1 ARM, 14 STR, 12 DEX, 11 WIL, Trident (d8)

Fish-Man Nobles: 4 HP, 0 ARM, 10 STR, 8 DEX, 12 WIL, Fishy Slap (d4)

King Fish-Man: 6HP, 1 ARM, 10 STR, 10 DEX, 15 WIL, Silver Fork (d6)

Electric Eel: 6HP, 0 ARM, 8 STR, 13 DEX, 10 WIL, Electric Shock (d6)
Critical Damage: If the victim is wearing metal then they take an extra d4 STR damage.
